\N<Luda Soldier>...Come out.

\N<Zozoie>Huh? What's with the suddenness? You got another woman lined
up for me?

\N<Zozoie>Heh, after all, that married woman last time was delicious,
so I'd like another one like that.

\N<Zuuteruka>Hey there, death row inmate, how's it going? Enjoying the
little time you have left in this world?

\N<Zozoie>What do you want, you? I didn't call for you. You're an
eyesore, get lost.

\N<Zuuteruka>The feeling of being an eyesore is mutual. And don't call me
"you."

\N<Zuuteruka>Watch your mouth, alright? Have you forgotten that I hold
the thread of your life in my hands?
\N<Zozoie>Is that all you wanted to say? What do you want with me?

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... I said I hold your life, didn't I? That's exactly
what I meant. You get it?
\N<Zuuteruka>Hey, take this guy away.
\N<Luda Soldier>Yes...
\N<Zozoie>...What are you planning to do?

\N<Zuuteruka>It's obvious, isn't it? You've gone too far. So now, you'll
gracefully accept your punishment.
\N<Zozoie>Wha... What the hell did I do?

\N<Zuuteruka>Listing all your crimes would be endless. Besides, leaving
you at large any longer puts women in danger.

\N<Zozoie>Are you talking about that married woman? What, are you in
love with her or something?

\N<Zozoie>Heh... This is a masterpiece! Is this what they call the
pathetic jealousy of a man?

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... Don't get cocky and misunderstand. I'm not putting
that woman on the stage of the training soldiers just to
break her.

\N<Zuuteruka>Well, even for you, it's a death sentence anyway. You've had
plenty of fun until now, haven't you?

\N<Zuuteruka>Surely you have no regrets? Dying with a smile and tears of
how fulfilling your life was?
\N<Zozoie>You... remember this, alright?

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, you're an idiot. As if I'd remember. After drinking
and sleeping, when I wake up, I won't even recall your
filthy face again.
\N<Zuuteruka>Did you think you were the center of the world or something?

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... If so, that's too bad. In the end, that's all you
ever were...
